(281, 5050877, ' <table class="table mail-table"> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-meta"> <tr> <td> <table class="table subject"> <tr> <td width="80" valign="top">发件人</td><td align="left">:&nbsp;教务处</td> <td align="right">发送时间&nbsp;&nbsp;:&nbsp;2014-01-02 15:09</td> </tr> <tr> <td width="80">主题</td> <td align="left" colspan=3>:&nbsp;期末考试温馨提示</td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-meta"> <tr> <td> <table class="table data"> <tr> <td width="80" align="left">附件文件</td> <td >&nbsp;</td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-content"> <tr> <td> <table class="table data"> <tr> <td> <div class="iframe-content"><P>&nbsp;</P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">全体考生：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">1．考生须持本人身份证和学生证（或身份证和学生卡），提前10分钟进入考场，按考场座位表对号入座，并将证件放在座位的右上角备查。无证件或持其他证件者不得参加考试。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">2．考生严禁携带移动通讯设备（手机等）进入考场，开考前应将非考试必需品，集中放在监考人员指定的地方，开考后若发现座位上、抽屉内有涉及与本场考试课程内容相关的物品（含书籍、讲义、笔记、手机、电子辞典等物品）或文字、公式（含在纸条、桌面上或抽屉内），不论抄袭与否，一律以考试违规论处。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">3．迟到30分钟以上者不得进入考场，开考30分钟后经监考人员允许方可离开考场。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">4．考生须严格遵守考场纪律，不得在考试过程中交谈、借用文具、窥视他人试卷，请勿做夹带、传递、交换、暗示、抄袭、带走试卷等舞弊行为。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">5．凡考试违纪舞弊者，学校将根据《广东金融学院学生考试违规处理办法》（详见附件），在两个工作日内作出相应处理，并进行通报批评。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">6．考试违规举报电话：37216153，举报电子邮箱：</SPAN><SPAN><A href="mailto:kwk@gduf.edu.cn"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; TEXT-DECORATION: underline; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘" class=15>kwk@gduf.edu.cn</SPAN></A></SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class=p0><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">最后，祝同学们期末考试取得优异的成绩！</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ‘仿宋_GB2312‘; FONT-SIZE: 14pt; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 27pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 28p