(297, 5121140, ' <table class="table mail-table"> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-meta"> <tr> <td> <table class="table subject"> <tr> <td width="80" valign="top">发件人</td><td align="left">:&nbsp;校学生会</td> <td align="right">发送时间&nbsp;&nbsp;:&nbsp;2014-03-06 16:11</td> </tr> <tr> <td width="80">主题</td> <td align="left" colspan=3>:&nbsp;致全校女生的倡议书</td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-meta"> <tr> <td> <table class="table data"> <tr> <td width="80" align="left">附件文件</td> <td >&nbsp;</td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <tr> <td> <table class="table mail-content"> <tr> <td> <table class="table data"> <tr> <td> <div class="iframe-content"><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"></SPAN>&nbsp;</P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">最美时光永存心</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">花开花落皆自在</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><?xml:namespace prefix = "o" ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">——致全校女生的倡议</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">亲爱的女同学们：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">英国小说家爱略特认为：“女人的希望是用阳光织成的，阴影就能使它们毁灭。”作为青年中的优秀群体，作为新时代自尊自爱自立自强的女大学生，我们应用新思想、真行动来抨击这种诋毁女性的谬论。我们不是旧时代只知女诫女工的“大家闺秀”。我们的人生里没有自怨自艾，我们不是别人的附属品，我们只属于我们自己。我们的希望像阳光一样炽烈，我们会追逐梦想，我们会谱写最美的青春乐章。乐章的跌宕起伏是不可避免的惊喜，被遮蔽的阴影在孕育着更激动人心的精彩。黯淡无光的人生不属于我们，只有流光溢彩的青春才是我们无悔的选择。让这份最美时光永远藏在心底，没有它，就没有凤凰磐涅的勇气，也没有“静观花开花落，笑看云卷云舒”的宁静。值我校第九届女生节之际，特向全体女同学发出如下倡议：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">一、珍惜时光，做最真实的自己。匆匆离去的时光带走了稚气、容颜，给予了阅历、慧美。珍藏一片冰心，坚守一份纯白岁月，把握青春里最美好的时光，珍惜身边的人与事，成为真、善、美的新时代女大学生。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">二、立足当下，做最自信的自己。繁华世界迷人心智，太多的梦想等着我们实现，太多的诱惑阻碍我们前进。树立正确的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">世界观、人生观&nbsp;、道德观、感情观</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">，用智慧和汗水浇灌成功之花。做生活中的强者，尊重生活、懂得生活、享受生活。在生活中展示风采、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">宣扬个性、挥洒青春、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">释放激情</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">，成就一段自尊自信自立自强的传奇佳话。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">三、宠辱不惊，做最勇敢的自己。花开花落终有时，了解规律，认清现实，乐观积极地面对生活中的挫折与磨难。坚定目标，无惧风雨，且行且珍惜。勇于登高，换来一片澄明天空，挣来一份光明前程。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">匆匆岁月磨平了棱角，浇灭了热情。在最美时光中寻回当初的雄心壮志，云淡风轻地看待生活中的跌宕起伏，整理行囊，勇敢地踏上未知旅程，享受每一次不同的体验，谱写一曲扣人心弦的青春旋律。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">校学生会</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=p0 style="MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 23pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘宋体‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘">2014年3月6日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ‘Calibri‘; mso-spacerun: ‘yes‘"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><!--EndFragment--></div> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table>', '', 0, 2, 1394118406, 1394520865),
